title: Price of tobacco sticks used with IQOS device from Phillip Morris in France 2019
xAxis: Tobacco sticks used with IQOS devices
summary: The Price tobacco in the used with was Tobacco Heets_Turquoise_Label_(61g)_20_units , who made 7 euros .
The most tobacco was Heets_Blue_Label_(62g)_20_units , with just 7 euros .

In second place was Tobacco Heets_Blue_Label_(61g)_20_units with 7 euros ; third place went to Tobacco Heets_Amber_Label_(61g)_20_units with 7 euros ; fourth place went to Tobacco Heets_Sienna_Label_(61g)_20_units with 7 euros and fifth place went to Tobacco Heets_Yellow_Label_(61g)_20_units , who was 7 euros .
gold: This statistic displays the price of tobacco sticks packs used with the IQOS smoking device from the brand Phillip Morris in France as of February 2019 . It shows that the Heets tobacco sticks were worth 7 euros per pack of 20 units .
